OL,3,CUS embassy racks up #14.6m in unpaid
OL,4,CLondon congestion charge fees
OL,6,FThe US embassy in London has racked up
OL,7,F#14.6 million in unpaid congestion
OL,8,Fcharge fees, figures show.
OL,10,FStatistics published by Transport for
OL,11,FLondon (TfL) revealed this is the most
OL,12,Famong all embassies in the capital.
OL,14,FThe Japanese embassy has the second
OL,15,Fhighest debt at #10.1 million,
OL,16,Ffollowed by the high commission of
OL,17,FIndia at #8.6 million.
OL,19,FAmong all embassies, the total is
OL,20,F#143.5 million.
