OL,3,CUS embassy racks up #14.6m in unpaid
OL,4,CLondon congestion charge fees
OL,6,FThe figures relate to unpaid fees and
OL,7,Ffines accrued by diplomats between the
OL,8,Flaunch of the congestion charge in
OL,9,F2003 and the end of last year.
OL,11,FBritish tax lawyer Dan Neidle said
OL,12,Fthere was a strong diplomats were
OL,13,Fexempt.
OL,15,FThe scheme involves a #15 daily fee
OL,16,Ffor driving within an area of central
OL,17,FLondon between 7am and 6pm on
OL,18,Fweekdays, and between noon and 6pm on
OL,19,Fweekends and bank holidays.
