OL,3,CUS embassy racks up #14.6m in unpaid
OL,4,CLondon congestion charge fees
OL,6,FThere are discounts and exemptions for
OL,7,Fvarious groups of people and vehicles,
OL,8,Fsuch as residents, taxis and fully
OL,9,Felectric cars.
OL,11,FTfL said in a statement: "We and the
OL,12,FUK Government are clear that the
OL,13,Fcongestion charge is a charge for a
OL,14,Fservice and not a tax.
OL,16,F"This means that diplomats are not
OL,17,Fexempt from paying it.
