OL,3,CUS embassy racks up #14.6m in unpaid
OL,4,CLondon congestion charge fees
OL,6,F"The majority of embassies in London
OL,7,Fdo pay the charge, but there remains a
OL,8,Fstubborn minority who refuse to do so,
OL,9,Fdespite our representations through
OL,10,Fdiplomatic channels.
OL,12,F"We will continue to pursue all unpaid
OL,13,Fcongestion charge fees and related
OL,14,Fpenalty charge notices, and are
OL,15,Fpushing for the matter to be taken up
OL,16,Fat the International Court of Justice."
OL,18,FThe US embassy in London, which moved
OL,19,Ffrom Grosvenor Square to Nine Elms in
OL,20,FJanuary 2018, was approached for a
OL,21,Fcomment.
